SGOCO Group, Ltd. Key Developments

SGOCO Group, Ltd.'s BOCA subsidiary Wins Contract to Build Hybrid Chiller Plant at Hong Kong International Airport
Jun 20 17
SGOCO Group, Ltd. announced that its BOCA subsidiary has signed a performance agreement with Hong Kong Aircraft Engineering Company Limited (HAECO) to design, supply and install a new ultra-high efficiency hybrid power chiller plant on a 10-year performance contract for HAECO's facility at the Hong Kong International Airport.


SGOCO Group, Ltd. announced delayed 20-F filing
Apr 28 17
On 04/28/2017, SGOCO Group, Ltd. announced that they will be unable to file their next 20-F by the deadline required by the SEC.


SGOCO Group, Ltd. Reports Unaudited Consolidated Earnings Results for the Six Months Ended June 30, 2016
Dec 23 16
SGOCO Group, Ltd. reported unaudited consolidated earnings results for the six months ended June 30, 2016. For the period, the company reported revenues of $4,678,000 against $504,000 a year ago. Loss from operations was $1,283,000 against $841,000 a year ago. Loss before provision for income taxes was $2,808,000 against $1,308,000 a year ago. Net loss was $2,703,000 or $0.42 per share basic and diluted against $1,308,000 or $0.30 per share basic and diluted a year ago. Net cash used in operating activities was $360,000 against net cash provided by operating activities of $190,000 a year ago.


